XERFONTS TITLE 'X E R F O N T S  ***  DISPLAY XEROX FONT'
         PUNCH ' ORDER XERFONTS(P) '  MAKE DUMPS EASIER
         PUNCH ' ALIAS LASFONTS,HPFONTS ' OTHER CODES
         PUNCH ' SETCODE AC(1)     '  LET @PRINTER ACCESS SYSOUT
         COPY  OPTIONGB
         GBLC  &DJDE
         SPACE 1
         SYSPARM LIST=YES
         SPACE 1
